2. cs.GR (Graphics): The paper deals with point clouds, which are commonly used in computer graphics for representing 3D objects. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The proposed method is data-driven and uses a deep network with graph convolution. This falls under the domain of machine learning.
